{{notability|date=July 2014}}
'''Dawson's Weekly''' is a six part series of half hour comedy plays, written by [[Ray Galton]] and [[Alan Simpson]], and starring [[Les Dawson]].<ref>Funny Way to be a Clown, John Fisher, Frederik Muller (1973), p.424</ref>

It ran from 12 June to 29 July 1975.<ref>The Trials and Triumphs of Les Dawson, Louis Barfe</ref>

